name: Elephant and Co. Anjuna, Goa

reviews.review_text:
A dog friendly bar, perfect when you want to chill with your furry friend !
The staff and owner were very welcoming. They have great seating and you can sit your pet right by your side !!
The Umami Butter mushrooms were scrumptious ! Wish we stayed back and tried more from their menu.
Until next time, cheers ECO !

We had a great time at the Elephant,  we had grilled tiger prawns and caramelised goats cheese with salad to start.
And then the Thai green prawn curry and Pan seared chonak, and the apple crumble.
Food was amazing in a fantastic location.
There was a singles dating evening on the night we went which was entertaining to watch.

Lazy lunch lazy ambiance at Elephant. Lovely view of the fields. Very village like. On the menu table today, squid rechado, pork belly burnt ends and pan seared chaunak fish. A meal second to none. Chef Walter did an excellent job.

description:
## Elephant and Co.: A Culinary Gem in Anjuna, Goa

Nestled in the scenic landscapes of Anjuna, Goa, Elephant and Co. has rapidly emerged as a local favorite, boasting an impressive **4.7 rating from over 1,071 reviews**. Often celebrated for its tranquil setting amidst verdant paddy fields, the restaurant is a dog-friendly enclave where patrons can enjoy delectable offerings while basking in a relaxed, casual atmosphere. The establishment is particularly renowned for its **chicken ghee roast**, **DJ evenings**, and the adding flair of **seafood delights**, such as **grilled tiger prawns** and **squid rechado**.

### Ambiance & Design

As you step into Elephant and Co., you’re greeted by an inviting vibe that seamlessly combines rustic charm with contemporary aesthetics. The restaurant features **spacious seating arrangements** that cater to both intimate meals and larger gatherings, often accompanied by soft lighting that enhances its laid-back demeanor. Reviews mention a **"lazy lunch ambiance"**, with scenic views of the surrounding fields, creating the perfect backdrop for a leisurely dining experience. The beautiful outdoor seating allows you to enjoy the refreshing Goan breeze, making it an ideal spot to reflect and unwind.

![Ambiance](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdlUO1A1NhLGyBF3E_L01imV9Ei4WRG7pG6ee0Oc9URJXEfFGhStm-qqvjNF3H4cpSJ1RxvUKoralSwsY0oidBzuykPNxO_V3Ck3uJffFH83B0Y84HoHSDBqXd1UdsCGWAT2sZTn-Q=w375-h281-p)

### Menu & Culinary Experience

The menu at Elephant and Co. is a delightful mélange of flavors that showcase both local Goan cuisine and globally inspired dishes. Signature offerings, such as **pan-seared chonak fish** and the ubiquitous **chicken ghee roast**, reflect the kitchen's commitment to quality ingredients and bold flavors. Notably, the **Umami Butter mushrooms** have quickly garnered praise, with one reviewer wishing they had sampled more of the eclectic menu during their visit. For those with a sweet tooth, the **apple crumble** is a must-try that perfectly caps off a meal.

Diners have lauded the meticulous presentation of dishes, which not only tantalize the taste buds but also please the eyes. Whether you are savoring **pork belly burnt ends** or a cooling **Thai green prawn curry**, the attention to detail is apparent, ensuring each dish is an experience in itself.

![Food Presentation](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdklOMjutzLZPAqr14ksNzY5iKKAHKvq_82OrpNS2IbDJW3qs1i9JktOj8PMtFiEV07DWI7nmhIaz95a2qR44fU-1YRctHe6AASk4KLW1lPIN-CfvWjEd8HdhfONda0h74K0RtQZ=w375-h281-p)

### Customer Experience & Service

The warm service at Elephant and Co. enhances the overall dining experience. Guests consistently describe the staff—owners included—as **welcoming and attentive**, ensuring diners feel right at home. Many patrons have noted the convenience of being able to bring their dogs along, underscoring the restaurant's pet-friendly policy. Such inclusivity creates a welcoming atmosphere for families and friends alike, whether you are a local or a traveler seeking a taste of Goan hospitality. 

### Popularity & Reviews

The restaurant has become quite the social hub, evidenced by its lively weekday events, including a **singles dating evening** that some guests found amusing and entertaining. The buzz around Elephant and Co. has garnered it a loyal following on social media, where foodies often share images and reviews. With a consistent delivery of quality food and enjoyable dining experiences, it’s no wonder this establishment has received praise not just from regular patrons but also from food critics in the area.

### Utilizing Visual Content

Captured through customer-shared images, the essence of Elephant and Co. is beautifully documented; the vibrant food presentations, charming décor, and lush surroundings come to life visually. Each shot conveys a sense of the restaurant's character and charm, from well-plated main courses to the inviting atmosphere that beckons diners to stay a while longer.

![Delicious Food](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/geougc-cs/AHRlGdkrTEc6Zqw2kOLISaCgw4YAouotyUfnQ89bwkW0CQ6DwpnAaJE9vIvHJZgUyJZ6zHHtZEgr_BvPOFpd2GYZDOQ6lQlr2sjoLm1AtrY7Zj-0Ybv9L9Ob0KxouYtwyharzyDoxDuW=w375-h281-p)

### Conclusion

In summary, Elephant and Co. stands out as a vibrant and dog-friendly dining destination in Anjuna, Goa, blending a unique culinary experience with a charming atmosphere. With its high ratings, diverse menu, and welcoming attitude, it's a place where good food, delightful company, and the serene outdoors come together beautifully. Whether you're indulging in a meal with friends, enjoying a day out with your furry companion, or simply basking in the laid-back vibe, Elephant and Co. is a stop worth making. With each review affirming its reputation, this eatery proves it has carved out a niche that resonates with both locals and visitors to the enchanting Goan coast.
